{"tid":1683132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋求法律援緩助","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:37:49.000Z","uid":195444,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0a98af07b1a69c9bedf9598d93ff41588dc114","tid":1683132,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:18:32.000Z","msg":"事源：我老公於15/10係將軍澳MTR對出呢間盈健醫務中心睇牙醫拔智慧齒.<br />\n之後拔完以為冇事照常番工啦.<br />\n點知拔智慧齒個半邊面越嚟越腫<br />\n痛到頂唔順走去複診,牙醫話係正常現象,複診咗兩次<br />\n有日番工真係痛到頂唔順啦,要搭的士去將軍澳醫院睇急症.個陣塊面已經腫到豬頭咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/30/210903_50669d061d083e20e38e423a95526bc1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F30%2F210903_50669d061d083e20e38e423a95526bc1.jpeg&h=da36d6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/30/210905_098a438ac87a6b4b77a47d27204a9a45.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F30%2F210905_098a438ac87a6b4b77a47d27204a9a45.jpeg&h=eba16653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來就發現細菌感染咗傷口,條頸去到口水腺同淋巴含膿要開刀,老公宜家係ICU插嗮喉<br />\n我希望可以將個位所謂既香港大學牙科學士個執照告到叮牌.<br />\n我唔明點解拔隻智慧齒可以拔到入ICU<br />\n大家引以為鑒千奇唔好幫儭呢間牙醫<br />\n我宜家好驚日日係咁喊.有冇法律界人士可以幫下我<br />\n留下我電話55438129<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzRfTM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzRfTM1.jpg&h=2c377dba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4Lo2Fn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4Lo2Fn.jpg&h=7279c91c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7OqwyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7OqwyJ.jpg&h=80acbf3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUJxV0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUJxV0p.jpg&h=360cfbfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"703a99be7e56bc6f48193b4e84bd6c41612e094e","tid":1683132,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:19:20.000Z","msg":"感謝同事借AC幫我開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42af12202fee36c5a12b689acac030febaecd501","tid":1683132,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"何[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/xZRfTQf.png[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZRfTQf.png%5B%2Fimg&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=34ff1445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/xZRfTQf.png[/img</a><br />\n大家認住呢間醫務中心<br />\n有咩病痛千奇唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6be9a347bde6f35974b9abacba400d26b2c216","tid":1683132,"uid":210233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"找區議員吧,選舉近,佢地實落力"},{"pid":"aa5a36614001ab1ff978506029d1f32c669188ed","tid":1683132,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"佢有冇開抗生素比你 拔完個陣"},{"pid":"87ec2e05403b0e05a75f11540bf1bb5479d5ba54","tid":1683132,"uid":166245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"無照xray就開刀？"},{"pid":"9cd0b1ac19d7d5534b515b374caa52dacdb2ec57","tid":1683132,"uid":236414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"搵區議員"},{"pid":"78c6b03dece571f801178a22f68a776a219e1cc3","tid":1683132,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"921cc501c4fb91c3a5f4215fd4958f703d6589b1","tid":1683132,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f6be9a347bde6f35974b9abacba400d26b2c216","tid":1683132,"uid":210233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"找區議員吧,選舉近,佢地實落力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"我只想我老公快啲好番出院<br />\n最緊要個人冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi